## 4. –°–¢–†–£–ö–¢–£–†–ê –ë–ê–ó–´ –î–ê–ù–ù–´–•

### 4.1. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `users`
```sql
id              BIGINT PRIMARY KEY (Telegram ID)
username        VARCHAR(255)
first_name      VARCHAR(255)
last_name       VARCHAR(255)
user_type       ENUM('horeca', 'retail')
establishment   VARCHAR(255)
registered_at   TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
last_activity   TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.2. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `promotions`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
title           VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
description     TEXT
image_url       VARCHAR(500)
user_type       ENUM('horeca', 'retail', 'all')
published_at    TIMESTAMP
is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
updated_at      TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.3. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `news`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
title           VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
description     TEXT
image_url       VARCHAR(500)
user_type       ENUM('horeca', 'retail', 'all')
published_at    TIMESTAMP
is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
updated_at      TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.4. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `deliveries`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
title           VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
description     TEXT
image_url       VARCHAR(500)
user_type       ENUM('horeca', 'retail', 'all')
published_at    TIMESTAMP
is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
updated_at      TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.5. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `mailings`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
text            TEXT NOT NULL
media_url       VARCHAR(500)
media_type      ENUM('photo', 'video', 'none')
target_type     ENUM('all', 'horeca', 'retail', 'custom')
scheduled_at    TIMESTAMP
sent_at         TIMESTAMP
status          ENUM('draft', 'scheduled', 'sent', 'cancelled')
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.6. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `mailing_stats`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
mailing_id      INT FOREIGN KEY
user_id         BIGINT FOREIGN KEY
sent_at         TIMESTAMP
opened_at       TIMESTAMP
clicked_at      TIMESTAMP
```

### 4.7. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `admin_users`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
username        VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL
password_hash   VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
role            ENUM('superadmin', 'admin', 'manager')
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
last_login      TIMESTAMP
is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
```

### 4.8. –¢–∞–±–ª–∏—Ü–∞ `activity_log`
```sql
id              INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
admin_id        INT FOREIGN KEY
action          VARCHAR(100)
details         TEXT
ip_address      VARCHAR(45)
created_at      TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
```

